segment.source: Use the Launch Applications page of the App-V sequencing wizard to run applications so that the Sequencer can optimize the package for streaming and you can configure how the application should be initially started on target computers.
segment.target: Use the Launch Applications page of the App-V sequencing wizard to run applications so that the Sequencer can optimize the package for streaming and you can configure how the application should be initially started on target computers.
